{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":{"id":"SitePage /posts/Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标/"}},"pageContext":{"url":"/posts/Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标/","relativePath":"posts/Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标.md","relativeDir":"posts","base":"Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标.md","name":"Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标","frontmatter":{"title":"Windows Phone 使用技巧-输入时移动光标","stackbit_url_path":"posts/Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标","date":"2013-01-04 02:13:59.4542834","excerpt":"","comments_count":0,"positive_reactions_count":0,"tags":["Windows phone","光标"],"canonical_url":"https://be-net.azurewebsites.net/post/2013/01/04/Windows-Phone-使用技巧-输入时移动光标","template":"post"},"html":"<h2><font color=\"#9b00d3\">一、问题：</font></h2>  <p>买了个Windows Phone Nokia Lumia 800，第一次用全触屏手机，碰到一个最大的操作难题，就是在写信息时，有时候需要把输入光标在文字间移来移去，定位到想要的位置上，并在那里插入新的文字。在以前的手机上，这根本不是问题，只需要按左键，光标就向左移动一个字符。按右键，光标便向右移动一个字符。可是，在Windows Phone上，就让人犯愁了，只能通过手指去按在目标位置。可是，手指很粗，字符很小，要将光标放置在想要位置上，总是非常困难，而且，很容易出现选中模式，若这时输入新的文字，老的文字便被覆盖了。</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE.jpg\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 353px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 166.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"屏幕截图\" title=\"屏幕截图\" src=\"/static/bb23ff64f065d5045542835e22e92742/51faa/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_thumb.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/bb23ff64f065d5045542835e22e92742/a80bd/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_thumb.jpg 148w,\n/static/bb23ff64f065d5045542835e22e92742/1c91a/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_thumb.jpg 295w,\n/static/bb23ff64f065d5045542835e22e92742/51faa/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_thumb.jpg 353w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 353px) 100vw, 353px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <h2><font color=\"#9b00d3\">二、解决方案：</font></h2>  <p>这也是我偶然发现的，哈哈。</p>  <p>1. 进入“设置”，“键盘”功能面板；</p>  <p>2. 勾选“日语12键”。</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(1).jpg\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 353px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 166.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"屏幕截图 (1)\" title=\"屏幕截图 (1)\" src=\"/static/02b07e88d3fb2f2b28cba02d4200c1f1/51faa/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(1)_thumb.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/02b07e88d3fb2f2b28cba02d4200c1f1/a80bd/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(1)_thumb.jpg 148w,\n/static/02b07e88d3fb2f2b28cba02d4200c1f1/1c91a/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(1)_thumb.jpg 295w,\n/static/02b07e88d3fb2f2b28cba02d4200c1f1/51faa/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(1)_thumb.jpg 353w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 353px) 100vw, 353px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <p>3. 输入时，当需要移动光标时，切换输入法到日文。就有向左向右移动输入光标的按键啦！</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(2).jpg\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 354px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 166.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"屏幕截图 (2)\" title=\"屏幕截图 (2)\" src=\"/static/cb4b76b1042cef6dec4c04b46b09d663/e1632/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(2)_thumb.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/cb4b76b1042cef6dec4c04b46b09d663/a80bd/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(2)_thumb.jpg 148w,\n/static/cb4b76b1042cef6dec4c04b46b09d663/1c91a/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(2)_thumb.jpg 295w,\n/static/cb4b76b1042cef6dec4c04b46b09d663/e1632/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%20(2)_thumb.jpg 354w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Ab